un m'hot ir untergetsundn.

446
00:20:37,101 --> 00:20:40,605
di vayb hot men untergetsundn oyfn tish, farbrent.

447
00:20:40,797 --> 00:20:42,678
un alemen...

448
00:20:41,134 --> 00:20:43,035
in ayere shtub?

449
00:20:42,678 --> 00:20:46,545
do- dos iz, neyn, dos iz mayn mishpokhe vos mir hobn im...

450
00:20:43,387 --> 00:20:44,264
dos...

451
00:20:46,888 --> 00:20:48,114
un er,

452
00:20:48,154 --> 00:20:51,523
un dernokh hot men alemen in di kleyne shtetlekh,

453
00:20:51,563 --> 00:20:55,219
glaykh alemen oysg- oysgeton zey naket,

454
00:20:55,292 --> 00:20:58,149
un zey hobn zikh aleyn oysgegrobn griber

455
00:20:58,149 --> 00:21:00,095
un zaynen arayn in di griber.

456
00:21:00,253 --> 00:21:05,142
 in di kleyne shtetlekh zaynen keyne yidn nit geblibn lebn.

457
00:21:04,776 --> 00:21:08,043
un dayn kuzin iz gekumen fun dort?

458
00:21:06,497 --> 00:21:10,721
⟨iz gekumen⟩ mayn ⟨s-⟩ kuzin hot zikh aroysgeganvet;

459
00:21:10,721 --> 00:21:12,566
er iz geven lebn grub,

460
00:21:12,792 --> 00:21:14,895
un er hot zikh aroysgeganvet,

461
00:21:14,935 --> 00:21:19,418
un er iz gekumen naketerheyt, in gatkes, in ŠIAULIAI.

462
00:21:19,845 --> 00:21:21,695
fun velekhe shtetl i-...?

463
00:21:19,896 --> 00:21:22,213
iz mayn mame in a kloyz...

464
00:21:22,213 --> 00:21:26,006
mayn mame hot zikh dervust az in Birzh hot zi gehat

465
00:21:26,006 --> 00:21:27,281
a kuzine,

466
00:21:27,321 --> 00:21:29,224
 iz zi avek in kloyz,

467
00:21:29,224 --> 00:21:34,706
un zi hot tsugenumen. er iz geven a gerateveter. er hot gehat a vayb mit kinder: alemen oysgeharget.

468
00:21:34,864 --> 00:21:37,068
iz er flegt shlofn oyfn tish.

469
00:21:37,092 --> 00:21:40,089
un mir zaynen geven in eyn kleynem tsimerl,

470
00:21:40,129 --> 00:21:42,485
zaynen mir geven tsen man efsher.

471
00:21:42,863 --> 00:21:47,734
un mayn meydele hot gezogt, "mame, vu hot men mir avekgeshtelt mayn sheyne bet?"

472
00:21:49,596 --> 00:21:51,007
un d⟨i an-⟩...

473
00:21:49,663 --> 00:21:53,150
zayn vayb hot men... in di kleyne shtetlekh

474
00:21:53,832 --> 00:21:56,509
iz keyn yid nit geblibn lebn,

475
00:21:56,633 --> 00:21:59,141
khibe di vos hobn zikh aroysgeganvet.

476
00:21:59,485 --> 00:22:03,647
s'iz gekumen fun Tavrik a mishpokhe, oykh nakete.

477
00:22:03,687 --> 00:22:05,486
ikh hob zey geholfn.

478
00:22:06,403 --> 00:22:09,569
vos zey zaynen gekumen in eyne hemder,

479
00:22:09,660 --> 00:22:13,783
vayle ale, di vos hobn zikh gekent a mol aroys⟨ra-⟩ fun grub...

480
00:22:13,783 --> 00:22:15,040
m'hot geshosn,

481
00:22:15,040 --> 00:22:17,113
hot men gemeynt az zey zaynen toyte,

482
00:22:17,575 --> 00:22:22,277
un dernokh zaynen zey ge- zey, zey iz nit f- arayngefaln di pulye,

483
00:22:22,485 --> 00:22:24,633
zaynen zey dernokh antlofn.

484
00:22:24,633 --> 00:22:28,790
dray getos iz geven in Lite, ⟨on eyn-hore⟩: Vilne,

485
00:22:28,847 --> 00:22:30,900
Kovne, un ŠIAULIAI.

486
00:22:31,058 --> 00:22:33,583
mer keyn getos iz nit geven.

487
00:22:33,606 --> 00:22:37,076
in ale kleyne shtetelekh, in Tavrik, in,

488
00:22:37,167 --> 00:22:40,935
in, Vilkomir, vu s'iz nor geven kleyne shtetlekh,

489
00:22:40,935 --> 00:22:44,400
hot men ale yidn avekgeshtelt bayn,

490
00:22:44,743 --> 00:22:47,842
bayn ⟨toy- me⟩, m'hot zey oysgeshosn...

491
00:22:47,842 --> 00:22:51,335
zey hobn aleyn zikh oysgegrobn di griber, un m'hot zey oysgeshosn.

492
00:22:51,409 --> 00:22:52,739
keyn yid iz nit,

493
00:22:52,739 --> 00:22:55,515
zeltn ver hot, ot di vos zaynen aroys.

494
00:22:55,476 --> 00:23:01,275
un bay andere mishpokhes iz oykh geven mentshn vos zey zenen antlofn, gekumen ⟨in⟩...?

495
00:23:00,252 --> 00:23:03,148
fun di, fun di shtetelekh?

496
00:23:02,395 --> 00:23:03,182
yo.

497
00:23:03,458 --> 00:23:08,481
un bay aykh, bay aykh iz geven der kuzin un nokh, tsvey?

498
00:23:03,525 --> 00:23:05,556
zeyer veynik UNK.

499
00:23:06,580 --> 00:23:08,559
der kuzin un ikh hob ge-

500
00:23:08,559 --> 00:23:12,550
un es hot zikh geratevet a Tavriker mishpokhe, fun Tavrik,

501
00:23:12,550 --> 00:23:13,998
oykh a shtetl.

502
00:23:14,028 --> 00:23:19,247
 hob ikh zey zeyer geholfn; kh'hob zey gegebn zakhn. un mayn kuzin iz geven bay mir.

503
00:23:19,422 --> 00:23:23,044
 iz gevezn parnose? dayn man hot nokh geARBEIT?

504
00:23:21,749 --> 00:23:25,456
 mayn, neyn, s'iz geven aza geshikhte:

505
00:23:25,716 --> 00:23:28,173
mayn man iz gegangen oyfn gas,

506
00:23:28,804 --> 00:23:31,683
un s'hobn im ongetrofn,

507
00:23:32,199 --> 00:23:34,907
 mayn man iz gegangen oyfn gas,

508
00:23:35,149 --> 00:23:37,674
un s'hobn im ongetrofn Litviner,

509
00:23:38,828 --> 00:23:40,965
un zey hobn im gefirt shisn.

510
00:23:41,933 --> 00:23:46,989
iz ongegangen der direktor fun, fun BATA's fabrik.

511
00:23:47,552 --> 00:23:51,292
er iz gevezn, er iz geven a Litviner, ⟨Shalkovs-⟩...

512
00:23:47,856 --> 00:23:49,183
fun di shukh-...?

513
00:23:51,366 --> 00:23:53,537
az er hot derzen mayn man,

514
00:23:53,560 --> 00:23:56,372
zogt er, "dem yidn muz ikh hobn."

515
00:23:56,580 --> 00:23:58,970
un er hot im geratevet fun toyt,

516
00:23:58,977 --> 00:24:01,502
un er hot im aroyfgefirt in fabrik.

517
00:24:01,660 --> 00:24:03,858
un mayn man hot di gantse tsayt,

518
00:24:03,858 --> 00:24:06,786
far, far ale groyse S.S.-layt

519
00:24:06,786 --> 00:24:09,889
hot er gemakht di modeln mit di shikh.

520
00:24:10,570 --> 00:24:14,209
ober dortn iz gevezn, dortn iz geven di S.S.

521
00:24:14,367 --> 00:24:19,187
un der, glavner direktor, der, der MENAHEL fun fabrik

522
00:24:19,227 --> 00:24:21,330
iz geven a S.S.-man.

523
00:24:22,129 --> 00:24:24,975
un az er flegt zen... un mayn man,

524
00:24:25,183 --> 00:24:27,624
az er hot gemakht baytelekh

525
00:24:27,917 --> 00:24:31,218
kedey dos tsu farkoyfn, mir zoln hobn tsum esn,

526
00:24:31,343 --> 00:24:35,167
flegt er zikh makhn nit visndik, vayl er hot im gedarft hobn.

527
00:24:36,220 --> 00:24:38,644
ober der, der, B⟨OLLEN⟩BACH,

528
00:24:39,004 --> 00:24:41,971
er iz geven a groyser S.S.-man.

529
00:24:41,971 --> 00:24:45,275
az er fleg geyn oyfn trep, flegn ale tsitern.

530
00:24:46,530 --> 00:24:49,477
ober tsu dayn man iz er gevezn gut?

531
00:24:48,049 --> 00:24:51,421
ts- nor tsu mayn man, vayle v- er iz geven a groyser,

532
00:24:51,421 --> 00:24:53,015
er hot im gemuzt hobn.

533
00:24:53,015 --> 00:24:54,995
er hot im eyn mol bashtroft;

534
00:24:55,305 --> 00:24:59,889
epes er hot im gezogt vos, tsi er hot nit derhert. hot er im aropgeshikt untn

535
00:25:00,216 --> 00:25:02,119
oyf shvartse arbet,

536
00:25:02,119 --> 00:25:06,605
un in a tog arum hot er im aroyfgenumen. er hot on im nit gekent oyskumen.

537
00:25:07,152 --> 00:25:09,340
hot men nokh gehat parnose.

538
00:25:09,257 --> 00:25:13,085
iz, y- ye, er flegt makhn baytelekh, mayn man.

539
00:25:13,564 --> 00:25:16,376
er flegt nit zen, er flegt dokh ⟨nit shteyn di gan-...⟩

540
00:25:16,467 --> 00:25:19,279
un er flegt, me flegt dos farkoyfn.

541
00:25:19,588 --> 00:25:23,311
iz, ⟨m- m- m-⟩ un fun dos hot men gegesn.

542
00:25:23,335 --> 00:25:28,071
vayl ikh bin nokh geven, ikh hob nokh nit gearbet, vayl ikh bin geven a shvangere.

543
00:25:28,701 --> 00:25:32,593
 itster bin ikh geshta- ⟨di⟩ gantse tsayt arumgegangen

544
00:25:32,667 --> 00:25:35,226
mit a, mit a breytn mantl,

545
00:25:35,299 --> 00:25:37,925
un ikh bin geven zeyer sheyn un yung.

546
00:25:38,100 --> 00:25:42,903
tsu farshteln, tsu farshteln di, az ir shvangert?

547
00:25:38,286 --> 00:25:40,524
hot men oyf mir nit...

548
00:25:40,656 --> 00:25:44,237
 y- ya, ikh, ikh bin dokh nit aroys,

549
00:25:44,260 --> 00:25:48,034
vayle di mishpokhe vos m'hot geshvangert hot men glaykh geshosn,

550
00:25:48,428 --> 00:25:51,004
in geto, s'iz dokh geshtanen postns.

551
00:25:51,195 --> 00:25:53,467
dernokh hobn mir gehat a khaver

552
00:25:53,912 --> 00:25:56,524
vos, arayngeyendik in geto

553
00:25:56,524 --> 00:25:59,002
flegt men alemen zeyer bazukhn.

554
00:26:00,122 --> 00:26:04,048
heyst dos, vos me trogt arayn, zey hobn nit gelozn arayntrogn.

555
00:26:04,543 --> 00:26:07,608
hot er anshtot eyn pekl tsigaretn

556
00:26:07,767 --> 00:26:11,591
arayngetrogn mistome tsen pe- tsen a pak.

557
00:26:12,340 --> 00:26:16,384
hot men im avekgeshtelt... Mazovetski iz geven zayn familye...

558
00:26:16,761 --> 00:26:19,742
hot men im avekgeshtelt oyfn plats,

559
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:23,117
far alemen in di oygn, un m'hot im oyfgehangen.

560
00:26:25,131 --> 00:26:29,718
far vo- vayle er hot arayngetrogn a gantsn pekl tsigaretn.

561
00:26:25,165 --> 00:26:26,171
vayl...

562
00:26:29,718 --> 00:26:32,583
nit eyn pekl, nor a gantsn pekl.

563
00:26:32,944 --> 00:26:36,144
vos flegt men arayntrogn? a por shtiklekh holts,

564
00:26:36,488 --> 00:26:38,642
a mol a shtikl broyt.

565
00:26:39,762 --> 00:26:43,564
ober dos, vayl er hot gehaltn a pekl tsigaretn,

566
00:26:43,564 --> 00:26:47,529
hot men im oyfgehangen oyfn plats far alemen in di oygn.

567
00:26:47,457 --> 00:26:49,172
du h- du host dos...

568
00:26:47,529 --> 00:26:51,071
a tate fun dray kinder. mir zaynen geshtanen un gekuk-...

569
00:26:50,663 --> 00:26:51,889
un gekukt.

570
00:26:51,071 --> 00:26:53,306
m'hot undz ekstre getsvungen kukn.

571
00:26:53,262 --> 00:26:54,724
getsvungen.

572
00:26:53,683 --> 00:26:58,335
aroysgenumen alemen fun di shtiber un m'hot undz getsvungen kukn.

573
00:26:57,649 --> 00:26:59,600
vos iz geven zayn nomen?

574
00:26:59,320 --> 00:27:01,460
Mazovetski.

575
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:01,761
Mazovetski.

576
00:27:01,460 --> 00:27:02,385
 ye.

577
00:27:02,712 --> 00:27:04,309
itster azoy,

578
00:27:04,669 --> 00:27:09,489
in geto bin ikh geven. dernokh iz gevorn di k- kinder-aktsye.

579
00:27:09,681 --> 00:27:14,235
eyn minut. ⟨ir hot⟩ geshvangert, ir hot geganen mit a mantl

580
00:27:13,967 --> 00:27:14,967
 ya.

581
00:27:14,235 --> 00:27:16,509
tsu fardekn dem shvanger?

582
00:27:15,773 --> 00:27:19,378
ya, ober ikh hob n- nit gekent geyn arbetn.

583
00:27:19,485 --> 00:27:21,992
ober mayn man iz geven in fabrik.

584
00:27:22,405 --> 00:27:25,301
dernokh iz geven di kinder-aktsye.

585
00:27:25,763 --> 00:27:28,305
velkhe tsayt? ven iz dos geven?

586
00:27:26,809 --> 00:27:30,435
 dos iz geven, in tsvey un fertsik, ⟨halt⟩...

587
00:27:30,673 --> 00:27:33,266
m'hot, m'hot tsugenumen di,

588
00:27:33,306 --> 00:27:37,506
m'iz arayngefo- m'hot tsugenumen di kinder mit di alte layt.

589
00:27:38,385 --> 00:27:43,205
iz in der fri, baginen, hot men zikh alemen geheysn onton.

590
00:27:43,853 --> 00:27:49,365
di vos, oyf arbet zaynen andere aroys, vayle di yingere flegn aroysgeyn,

591
00:27:49,607 --> 00:27:54,039
ober eltere froyen un kinder zaynen dokh geblibn in geto.

592
00:27:54,754 --> 00:27:58,224
s'zaynen arayngeforn groyse AVTOBUSn

593
00:27:59,530 --> 00:28:03,557
un m'hot genumen fun yeder shtub shlepn di alte

594
00:28:04,086 --> 00:28:08,518
m⟨e-⟩ di eltere mentshn mit di kinder in di, in di OTOs.

595
00:28:09,165 --> 00:28:13,782
mir hobn gehat, s'iz geven bay undz dokter Lunts, a froyen-dokter,

596
00:28:14,211 --> 00:28:16,112
un er hot gehat a vayb

597
00:28:16,472 --> 00:28:18,963
vos zi hot gekent ale shprakhn.

598
00:28:20,303 --> 00:28:24,009
iz der, der lager-firer, az er fleg kumen,

599
00:28:24,505 --> 00:28:26,417
flegt er reydn mit ir...

600
00:28:26,417 --> 00:28:30,894
zi hot geredt perfekt daytsh... vos er hot gedarft, der lager-firer, der daytsh.

601
00:28:31,013 --> 00:28:34,033
 un zi hot gehat a meydele oykh.

602
00:28:34,410 --> 00:28:36,648
flegt er shtendik brengen

603
00:28:36,722 --> 00:28:38,994
far di meydele shokoladn.

604
00:28:40,384 --> 00:28:42,875
un beshas s'iz gevorn di aktsye

605
00:28:43,337 --> 00:28:46,756
iz zi aroys oyfn plats un m'hot gekhapt ir kind.

606
00:28:46,898 --> 00:28:51,493
zogt zi oyf rusish, "NE STRELYAYTE MENYA, YA NE KHOCHU!"

607
00:28:51,493 --> 00:28:52,759
di meydele.

608
00:28:52,759 --> 00:28:55,636
iz zi gefaln im tsu di fis kushn dem,

609
00:28:55,636 --> 00:28:59,413
vos er flegt ale tog kumen un brengen di meydl shokolad.

610
00:28:59,605 --> 00:29:01,228
hot er gezogt,

611
00:29:01,461 --> 00:29:03,615
"gezets iz gezets.

612
00:29:03,857 --> 00:29:08,120
mir hobn a gezets." un m'hot di meydl arayngevorfn oykh in OTO.

613
00:29:08,143 --> 00:29:09,136
ikh vil,

614
00:29:09,136 --> 00:29:12,829
ir zo-, undz endik'mir dize kasete,

615
00:29:12,666 --> 00:29:13,671
vos?

616
00:29:12,868 --> 00:29:13,599
un...

617
00:29:13,599 --> 00:29:16,078
dize kasete endikt zikh yetst,

618
00:29:16,078 --> 00:29:19,106
un mir veln redn in di tsveyte kasete.

619
00:29:18,977 --> 00:29:20,978
in a tsveyte kasete?

620
00:29:20,057 --> 00:29:21,113
ya.

